(b-a)^2\int_a^bf'^2(x)dx\ge (b-a)\int_{a}^{x_0}1dx\int_a^{x_0}f'^2(x)dx\ge(b-a)\left(\int_a^{x_0}f'(x)dx\right)^2
=M^2(b-a)\ge \int_a^bf^2(x)dx
\int_a^bf^2(x)dx=\int_a^b\left(\int_a^x f'(y)dy\right)^2dx
\left(\int_a^x f'(y)dy\right)^2\leq \int_a^x[f'(y)]^2dy\int_a^x1dy=(x-a)\int_a^x[f'(y)]^2dy
\begin{align} \int_a^bf^2(x)dx &\leq \int_a^b(x-a)\int_a^x [f'(y)]^2dydx\\ &\leq \int_a^b(b-a)\int_a^b [f'(y)]^2dydx=(b-a)^2\int_a^b [f'(y)]^2dy \end{align}
