 \int_a^b f(x)^2 dx \leq (b-a)\left[\int_a^b f(x)^2dx\right]^{\frac{1}{2}}\left[\int_a^b f'(x)^2 dx\right]^{\frac{1}{2}} 
F(x)=\int_{a}^{x}f(t)dt
|F(x)|\le\int_{a}^{b}|f(t)|dt\le(b-a)^{\frac{1}{2}}\left(\int_{a}^{b}f^2(t)dt\right)^{\frac{1}{2}}
\int_{a}^{b}f^2(x)dx=-\int_{a}^{b}F(x)f'(x)dx\le (b-a)^2\int_{a}^{b}[f'(x)]^2dx
\displaystyle\;\;\lambda = \frac{\pi}{b-a}.\;\;
f(a) = f(b) = 0
f \in C^1[a,b]
